    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/de0bc37a6ceeb59b56aa47c0cd6b285a.poster.avif?t=1757564270\" width=320 height=86 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/de0bc37a6ceeb59b56aa47c0cd6b285a.webm?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/de0bc37a6ceeb59b56aa47c0cd6b285a.mp4?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这款受到《Project Zomboid》、《RimWorld》、《Zero Sievert》和《逃离塔科夫》启发的自上而下的抽取射击游戏中，探索、潜行和掠夺经过程序生成的社区。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实时数百只僵尸！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/34d2602d63eca62dcd16337a736ace42.poster.avif?t=1757564270\" width=590 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/34d2602d63eca62dcd16337a736ace42.webm?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/34d2602d63eca62dcd16337a736ace42.mp4?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于网格的库存系统</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/f883d49470351a98fb89200c155cc879.poster.avif?t=1757564270\" width=466 height=588 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/f883d49470351a98fb89200c155cc879.webm?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/f883d49470351a98fb89200c155cc879.mp4?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逼真的视线/战争迷雾系统</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/cca788f74d8dd49dfc59ac86289c43be.poster.avif?t=1757564270\" width=590 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/cca788f74d8dd49dfc59ac86289c43be.webm?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360880/extras/cca788f74d8dd49dfc59ac86289c43be.mp4?t=1757564270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>关注我的Twitch频道获取开发流程或YouTube频道上的更新！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><br>在《Project Zomboid》、《逃离塔科夫》、《Zero Sievert》等游戏中度过了数千个小时后，我受到启发并致力于开发一款结合了我最感兴趣的元素的游戏。我从2021年初开始着手这个项目。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 游戏将保持《Zomboid》中的沉浸感和大量僵尸，但我也不想整天都要投入到游戏中。<br></li><li> 《逃离塔科夫》中的高风险库存和装备系统意味着你不能随便带入物品。无论你带走什么，都要做好失去一切的准备。<br></li><li> 情绪和健康系统结合了《Zomboid》和《RimWorld》的要素。在野外，你需要管理体力消耗、环境因素和负重能力。<br></li><li> 在家中，幸存者将努力建造你设置的蓝图，烹饪和管理食物，照顾受伤者，并建设防御设施。<br></li><li> 在家中，殖民者的情绪会影响他们在野外的表现。今天没有好好吃饭吗？或者因为殖民地无事可做而心情糟糕？你今天射击的准确度就不会那么好。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 程序生成的房屋<br></li><li> 程序生成的社区<br></li><li> 属性系统-管理饥饿、口渴、无聊、疲劳<br></li><li> 家园系统-为殖民者建造和制作住所<br></li><li> 战斗系统-近战和枪支<br></li><li> 枪支附件系统<br></li><li> 幸存者关系系统。你在殖民地得罪了某个人？他们可能会偷走你的战利品并离开。<br></li><li> 模组支持</li></ul>",
